title: 80s Prom Party
desc: Dust off your best taffeta dress and ruffled shirt... 80s Prom is back to our old home at the Fonda Theatre. Taking place Feb 6th, we'll have a dj, band, photo booths, and hundreds of people rocking out to 80s music. For more information and to purchase tickets, go to www.80spromparty.com . ?Event is 21 and over.? Tickets can not be refunded after Monday, Feb 1st
